Package: update-from-usb-media
Architecture: all
Depends: mount-usb-media, ${misc:Depends}
Conflicts: update-from-added-sources, add-iso-sources
Replaces: update-from-added-sources, add-iso-sources
Description: Potentially update from USB media
 Scan newly arriving USB media for ISO format files containing an APT archive,
 and perform a software update if an archive is found.
